<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #141414;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #e50914;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #e50914;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #b3b3b3;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e50914, #ff6b00);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #2d2d2d;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid #444;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.3);
        }
        
        .server-info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .actions {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p><%= message %></p>
        <p>Halaman yang Anda cari mungkin telah dipindahkan, dihapus, atau tidak pernah ada.</p>
        
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Kembali ke Beranda
            </a>
            <a href="/api/health" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> Cek Status Server
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="server-info">
            <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> DramaChina Streaming â€¢ <%= new Date().toLocaleString() %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
